from file buf
C-x C-s                 save file
C-x C-c                 close emacs
C-x C-e                 evaluate the form before cursor
                        and print result at status line
M-x slime RET           open repl
C-c C-c                 send outermost form to repl
C-c C-z                 move cursor to repl buf

from repl buf
,quit RET               close repl and all its buf

from error buf
q                       close current buf
